and solve their problems.

134
00:12:35.356 --> 00:12:36.725
A cult?

135
00:12:36.790 --> 00:12:38.192
It's pretty common
around here.

136
00:12:38.259 --> 00:12:39.994
Even the president
is a Marialioncero.

137
00:12:40.060 --> 00:12:41.395
-Mm.
-It's bullshit.

138
00:12:41.462 --> 00:12:44.131
But they can't move here.

139
00:12:44.198 --> 00:12:47.401
