974
01:18:11.158 --> 01:18:12.793
Oh. God.
She's just a kid.

975
01:18:12.860 --> 01:18:15.329
We have to kill the body.
or he will kill us.

976
01:18:18.365 --> 01:18:21.536
What if--what if we
offer it a new body.

977
01:18:21.603 --> 01:18:23.737
